{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MZeN5x941SN9UtJQefNzkt","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me compile my findings into a comprehensive report.\n\n## Summary of Ed25519 and Signature Verification Libraries in the Monorepo\n\nBased on my thorough search of `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/`, here are my findings:\n\n### 1. **Ed25519/Signature Libraries Present**\n\n**NOT directly available in the monorepo:**\n- `tweetnacl` - Not found in any package.json\n- `@noble/ed25519` - Not found in any package.json\n- `@noble/curves` - Not found in any package.json (though installed as a transitive dependency)\n\n**AVAILABLE (via transitive dependencies):**\n- `@noble/hashes` ^1.6.0 - Explicitly required by `@rng-utopia/fairness`\n- `@noble/curves` - Installed as a transitive dependency (likely from `@solana/web3.js`)\n\n### 2. **Existing Ed25519 Signature Verification Code**\n\nNo Ed25519 signature verification code exists in the codebase. What does exist:\n\n**Fairness Verification** (`packages/fairness/`):\n- Uses `@noble/hashes` for SHA-256 and HMAC-SHA256\n- `/src/commitment.ts` - Verifies commitments via SHA256\n- `/src/crash.ts` - Uses HMAC-SHA256 for crash point computation\n- `/src/verification.ts` - Verifies round fairness by comparing hashes\n\n**Coinflip Verification** (`apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/`):\n- `/verification.ts` - Verifies coinflip matches using:\n  - Event parsing from blockchain transactions\n  - SHA-256 verification (custom implementation in `/crypto.ts`)\n  - Result hash validation\n- `/crypto.ts` - Custom crypto utilities for SHA-256 (via Web Crypto API)\n\n**Lord of RNGs Verification** (`apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/utils/`):\n- `/verification.ts` - Verifies lord rounds via event parsing\n- Reads VRF randomness from on-chain accounts\n\n### 3. **@solana/web3.js Capabilities**\n\n`@solana/web3.js` ^1.98.0 is installed in multiple packages:\n- `apps/platform`\n- `services/backend`\n- `solana/` (node workspace)\n- `packages/wallet`\n- `packages/game-engine`\n- `packages/anchor-client`\n\n**Important:** `@solana/web3.js` does NOT export nacl/ed25519 as public APIs. It uses nacl internally (bundled as `tweetnacl` dependency) but doesn't expose signature verification functions to consumers. For Ed25519 verification, you would need to add `tweetnacl`, `@noble/curves`, or `@solana/web3.js` nacl (if you can access it).\n\n### **Package Dependency Summary**\n\n| Package | Has ED25519 | Has Crypto |\n|---------|------------|-----------|\n| `@rng-utopia/fairness` | No | `@noble/hashes` ✓ |\n| `@rng-utopia/platform` | No | `@solana/web3.js`, custom SHA256 |\n| `@solana/web3.js` | Bundled (internal) | Yes (internal) |\n| `@rng-utopia/backend` | No | `@solana/web3.js` |\n| `@rng-utopia/wallet` | No | `@solana/web3.js` |\n\n**Files with cryptographic operations:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/fairness/src/commitment.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/fairness/src/crash.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/crypto.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/utils/verification.ts`"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a66a0ecceafabb085 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 55736\ntool_uses: 37\nduration_ms: 104948</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"612240eb-bf1a-44cf-9ae4-1551e7c0525e","uuid":"7dc6b4d6-b05c-4875-bd13-c530859287f5","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Check what Ed25519 verification libraries are available in the monorepo at /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/. Specifically:\n1. Is `tweetnacl` or `@noble/ed25519` or `@noble/curves` already in any package.json?\n2. Is there any existing Ed25519 signature verification code in the codebase?\n3. Check if `@solana/web3.js` has nacl/ed25519 capabilities that could be used.\n\nSearch for patterns like \"nacl\", \"ed25519\", \"tweetnacl\", \"noble\" in package.json files and source code. Thoroughness: medium","agentId":"a66a0ecceafabb085","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me compile my findings into a comprehensive report.\n\n## Summary of Ed25519 and Signature Verification Libraries in the Monorepo\n\nBased on my thorough search of `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/`, here are my findings:\n\n### 1. **Ed25519/Signature Libraries Present**\n\n**NOT directly available in the monorepo:**\n- `tweetnacl` - Not found in any package.json\n- `@noble/ed25519` - Not found in any package.json\n- `@noble/curves` - Not found in any package.json (though installed as a transitive dependency)\n\n**AVAILABLE (via transitive dependencies):**\n- `@noble/hashes` ^1.6.0 - Explicitly required by `@rng-utopia/fairness`\n- `@noble/curves` - Installed as a transitive dependency (likely from `@solana/web3.js`)\n\n### 2. **Existing Ed25519 Signature Verification Code**\n\nNo Ed25519 signature verification code exists in the codebase. What does exist:\n\n**Fairness Verification** (`packages/fairness/`):\n- Uses `@noble/hashes` for SHA-256 and HMAC-SHA256\n- `/src/commitment.ts` - Verifies commitments via SHA256\n- `/src/crash.ts` - Uses HMAC-SHA256 for crash point computation\n- `/src/verification.ts` - Verifies round fairness by comparing hashes\n\n**Coinflip Verification** (`apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/`):\n- `/verification.ts` - Verifies coinflip matches using:\n  - Event parsing from blockchain transactions\n  - SHA-256 verification (custom implementation in `/crypto.ts`)\n  - Result hash validation\n- `/crypto.ts` - Custom crypto utilities for SHA-256 (via Web Crypto API)\n\n**Lord of RNGs Verification** (`apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/utils/`):\n- `/verification.ts` - Verifies lord rounds via event parsing\n- Reads VRF randomness from on-chain accounts\n\n### 3. **@solana/web3.js Capabilities**\n\n`@solana/web3.js` ^1.98.0 is installed in multiple packages:\n- `apps/platform`\n- `services/backend`\n- `solana/` (node workspace)\n- `packages/wallet`\n- `packages/game-engine`\n- `packages/anchor-client`\n\n**Important:** `@solana/web3.js` does NOT export nacl/ed25519 as public APIs. It uses nacl internally (bundled as `tweetnacl` dependency) but doesn't expose signature verification functions to consumers. For Ed25519 verification, you would need to add `tweetnacl`, `@noble/curves`, or `@solana/web3.js` nacl (if you can access it).\n\n### **Package Dependency Summary**\n\n| Package | Has ED25519 | Has Crypto |\n|---------|------------|-----------|\n| `@rng-utopia/fairness` | No | `@noble/hashes` ✓ |\n| `@rng-utopia/platform` | No | `@solana/web3.js`, custom SHA256 |\n| `@solana/web3.js` | Bundled (internal) | Yes (internal) |\n| `@rng-utopia/backend` | No | `@solana/web3.js` |\n| `@rng-utopia/wallet` | No | `@solana/web3.js` |\n\n**Files with cryptographic operations:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/fairness/src/commitment.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/fairness/src/crash.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/crypto.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/utils/verification.ts`"}],"totalDurationMs":104948,"totalTokens":55736,"totalToolUseCount":37,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":842,"cache_read_input_tokens":53825,"output_tokens":1068,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":842},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"